# Brainstorm Report: Record Screens UI Redesign

**Date:** 2025-01-07
**Task:** Redesign recordings list và detail screens với 3 tabs (Phiên âm, Tóm tắt, Chat AI)

---

## 1. Current State Analysis

### RecordingsTab (recordings_tab.dart)
- Simple ListView với cards hiển thị title, date, duration
- Status badge "Summarized" / "Not summarized"
- FloatingActionButton với icon mic
- Thiếu: Header styling, play button trên card, shadow/ring effects

### RecordDetailScreen (record_detail_screen.dart)
- Standard AppBar với title và more options
- Player card với progress slider và controls
- Summary sections hiển thị dạng text blocks
- Thiếu: Tab navigation, transcript view, chat AI interface

---

## 2. Design Requirements từ HTML Mockups

### RecordList.html
```
Header:
├── Title "Ghi âm" (h1, font-bold text-2xl)
├── Subtitle "4 bản ghi gần đây"
└── Search button (rounded-full)

Recording Card:
├── Title (font-bold text-base)
├── Date • Duration (text-xs)
├── More button (more_vert)
├── Status badge với icon:
│   ├── "Đã tóm tắt" (emerald, check_circle)
│   └── "Chưa tóm tắt" (amber, hourglass_top)
└── Play button (rounded-full, hover:bg-primary)

Floating Button:
└── size-16, rounded-[20px], ring-4 ring-white/20
```

### RecordDetail.html + Tabs
```
AppBar:
├── Back button (arrow_back)
├── Title (centered, truncate)
└── More button (more_vert)

File Info:
├── Filename (text-xl font-bold)
└── Date (text-sm text-gray-500)

Tab Bar (grid-cols-3):
├── "Phiên âm" (transcript)
├── "Tóm tắt" (summary)
└── "Chat AI" (chat)

Bottom Player (absolute bottom-0):
├── Edit & Share buttons (grid-cols-2)
├── Progress bar
├── Time labels (11:43 / 35:10)
└── Controls: replay_10, play/pause, forward_10
```

### RecordSummarizeTab.html
```
Header: "Được tạo bởi AI" + Copy button

Sections:
├── Điểm chính (lightbulb, indigo)
│   └── Bullet list items
├── Quyết định (verified, emerald)
│   └── Checkmark list items
└── Mục hành động (assignment_turned_in, amber)
    └── Checkbox items với assignee và deadline
```

### RecordChatAITab.html
```
Messages:
├── AI message (left align):
│   ├── Avatar (gradient blue-indigo, smart_toy)
│   ├── Label "AI Assistant"
│   └── Bubble (bg-card-dark, rounded-2xl rounded-tl-none)
└── User message (right align):
    ├── Bubble (bg-primary, rounded-2xl rounded-tr-none)
    └── Timestamp

Suggested Replies:
└── Horizontal scrollable chips

Input Bar:
├── Add button (add_circle)
├── Input field (rounded-[24px])
├── Mic button
└── Send button (bg-primary, rounded-full)
```

---

## 3. Implementation Approaches

### Approach A: Single Screen với TabController
**Pros:**
- State management đơn giản
- Smooth tab switching với animation
- Player controls persist across tabs

**Cons:**
- File có thể lớn nếu nhiều logic

**Implementation:**
```dart
class RecordDetailScreen extends StatefulWidget
    with SingleTickerProviderStateMixin {
  late TabController _tabController;

  Widget build() {
    return Column(
      children: [
        _buildTabBar(),
        Expanded(
          child: TabBarView(
            children: [
              TranscriptTab(),
              SummaryTab(),
              ChatAITab(),
            ],
          ),
        ),
        _buildBottomPlayer(),
      ],
    );
  }
}
```

### Approach B: Separate Tab Widgets
**Pros:**
- Clean separation of concerns
- Easier testing per tab
- Reusable components

**Cons:**
- Need state management cho chat history
- Phải pass recording data xuống tabs

**File Structure:**
```
lib/screens/recording/
├── record_detail_screen.dart (main + tab controller)
├── tabs/
│   ├── transcript_tab.dart
│   ├── summary_tab.dart
│   └── chat_ai_tab.dart
└── widgets/
    ├── audio_player_bar.dart
    ├── summary_section_card.dart
    ├── chat_message_bubble.dart
    └── suggested_reply_chip.dart
```

### Approach C: Custom Tab Indicator (Pill Style)
HTML mockup dùng pill-style tabs không phải underline:
```dart
Container(
  padding: EdgeInsets.all(4),
  decoration: BoxDecoration(
    color: AppColors.cardDark.withOpacity(0.6),
    borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(12),
  ),
  child: Row(
    children: [
      _buildTabButton('Phiên âm', 0),
      _buildTabButton('Tóm tắt', 1),
      _buildTabButton('Chat AI', 2),
    ],
  ),
)
```

---

## 4. Recommended Implementation Plan

### Phase 1: Update RecordingsTab
1. Update header với new styling (title, subtitle, search button)
2. Redesign card layout:
   - Title + more button row
   - Date • Duration row
   - Status badge + play button row
3. Update FAB styling (rounded-[20px], ring effect)
4. Localize text to Vietnamese

### Phase 2: Restructure RecordDetailScreen
1. Create custom pill-style TabBar
2. Move player controls to sticky bottom bar
3. Extract tabs into separate widgets
4. Update AppBar styling

### Phase 3: Implement TranscriptTab
1. Empty state với icon và CTA button
2. Transcript view với timestamps (future)

### Phase 4: Implement SummaryTab
1. Create SummarySection widget với colored headers
2. Implement KeyPoints section (bullet list)
3. Implement Decisions section (checkmark list)
4. Implement ActionItems section (checkbox list với assignee)
5. Add copy button functionality

### Phase 5: Implement ChatAITab
1. Chat message list với AI/User bubbles
2. AI avatar với gradient
3. Suggested reply chips (horizontal scroll)
4. Input bar với add, mic, send buttons
5. Mock chat responses for demo

### Phase 6: Bottom Player Bar
1. Progress bar styling
2. Time labels
3. Control buttons (replay_10, play/pause, forward_10)
4. Edit & Share action buttons

---

## 5. New Files to Create

```
lib/screens/recording/tabs/
├── transcript_tab.dart
├── summary_tab.dart
└── chat_ai_tab.dart

